output_list.criticism: The setAIRDROPBounce function has an integer overflow in the calculation of AIRDROPBounce * 1e8. This can lead to incorrect results and potential loss of funds.
The setICORatio function has an integer overflow in the calculation of ICORatio * 1e144. This can lead to incorrect results and potential loss of funds.
The setMINfinney function has an integer overflow in the calculation of MINfinney * 1e18. This can lead to incorrect results and potential loss of funds.
The disablePurchasing function has an integer overflow in the calculation of totalSupply - totalContribution. This can lead to incorrect results and potential loss of funds.
